author: stefan2
msg: On the fsfs-format7 branch:  Address an inefficiency in out aligned
buffer access strategy.  Attempt an aligned buffer read whenever
the current location is outside the desired block.  Otherwise, the
next block will not be read when linearly traversing the file.
